<exercise id="fs-id1450214" type="ap-test-prep"><problem id="fs-id2378963">
<para id="fs-id2641681">When two neutral objects are rubbed against each other, the first one gains a net charge of 3<emphasis effect="italics">e.</emphasis> Which of the following statements is true?</para>
