<problem id="fs-id3318421">
<para id="fs-id3187677">In an experiment, a student runs a comb through his hair several times and brings it close to small pieces of paper. Which of the following will he observe?</para>
<list id="fs-id2066441" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha" mark-prefix="(" mark-suffix=")">
