<exercise id="fs-id1860256" type="ap-test-prep"><problem id="fs-id1924498">
<para id="fs-id2334790">The charges on two identical metal spheres (placed in a closed system) are -2.4×10<sup>−17</sup> C and -4.8×10<sup>−17</sup> C.</para>
